            <p>Environment - Windows 10 Google Chrome Version 104.0.5112.81</p>

<p>Steps to reproduce:</p>

<ol>
	<li>Open <a href="https://portal.bc.bulcode.com/" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">https://portal.bc.bulcode.com/</a></li>
	<li>Click the round icon with a man in the right corner of the page</li>
	<li>Click Profile</li>
	<li>Click Information</li>
	<li>Click the Spoken languages field</li>
	<li>Check some language, e.g. Spanish</li>
	<li>Click Update</li>
	<li>Click Companies on the left side of the page</li>
	<li>Click Search</li>
	<li>Click <a href="https://portal.bc.bulcode.com/view/company/1ecf2eff-8540-68de-ad12-efabbcccd7cb" class="external-link" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Company 100000002</a></li>
	<li>Click Employees</li>
	<li>Find Petya Petrova (see also other employees)</li>
</ol>


<p>Expected result:</p>

<p><b>We should see all the spoken languages.</b></p>

<p>Actual result:</p>

<p><b>We see just the last added spoken language.</b></p>

<p>Suggestion: If an employee speaks several languages, it would be better to show them all, not just 1 of them. </p>
